    <h2 class="card-title">International Vitamin Corporation - GNC Holdings, Inc.<span id="lblMatterID"> (095077-10020)</span>                    </h2>                </div>                <div class="col-md-2">                    <button id="btnMoreDetails" type="button" class="btn btn-si btn-primary moredetails" style="float: right;" data-target="#dealModal" data-id="095077-10020">More manufacturer and distributor of dietary supplements, in a joint venture transaction with GNC. GNC formed a bankruptcy-remote entity to which it contributed 100% of the equity of target, Nutra Manufacturing, Inc. IVC initially acquired 57.14% of target from GNC, and will acquire the remaining equity in target via four mandatory subsequent transactions over four years. GNC and target entered into a long-term supply agreement. Additionally, target acquired GNC's leasehold rights in a manufacturing facility, and target leased back a portion of the facility to GNC for continued use.  </div>            <div class="card-subsection">               <div class="col-sm-6">                            <div class="form-group row">                               <label for="lblPurchasePrice" class="col-md-4 col-form-label" id="lblPurchasePriceLabel">Deal Value:</label>                                <div class="col-md-8">                                    <span id="lblPurchasePrice">$176,000,000</span>                                </div>                            </div>                            <div class="form-group row ClientRepresentationSection ">                                <label for="lblClientRepresentation" class="col-md-4 col-form-label">Client Representation:</label>                                <div class="col-md-8">                                    <span id="lblClientRepresentation">Joint Venturer (JV)</span>                                 </div>                            </div>                            <div class="form-group row">                                <label for="lblFoundationIndustry1" class="col-md-4 col-form-label">Foundation Industry:</label>                               <div class="col-md-8">                                   <span id="lblFoundationIndustry1">Life Sciences/Life Sciences Companies/Consumer Health;     <script type="text/javascript">



        $(document).ready(function () {

            //$('.js-tooltip').tooltip();
            $(".searchcriteria")
                .change(function () {
                    searchDeals();
                });

            $(".searchcriteriamultiple").change(function () {
                searchDeals();
            });
            initPage();


            var selectedSearch = $('#selectedSearch').val();
            var toggleSectionVal = "btnMAPE";
            if (selectedSearch != "") {
                toggleSectionVal = selectedSearch;
            }
            toggleSection(toggleSectionVal);

            // Copy to clipboard
            // Grab any text in the attribute 'data-copy' and pass it to the 
            // copy function
            $('.js-copy').click(function () {
                event.preventDefault();
                //var text = $(this).attr('data-copy');
                var linkText = $('#txtSearchLink').val();

                if (linkText != null && linkText != "") {
                    var el = $(this);
                    copyToClipboard(linkText, el);
                }
                //else {
                //    alert("No link to copy");
                //}
                return false;
            });


            // Get the input field
            (function () {
                var txtTextSearch = document.getElementById('txtTextSearch');
                txtTextSearch.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });

                var txtNumberofBlockersinSellerStructureStart = document.getElementById('txtNumberofBlockersinSellerStructureStart');
                txtNumberofBlockersinSellerStructureStart.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });

                var txtNumberofBlockersinSellerStructureEnd = document.getElementById('txtNumberofBlockersinSellerStructureEnd');
                txtNumberofBlockersinSellerStructureEnd.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });

                var signingDateStart = document.getElementById('signingDateStart');
                signingDateStart.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });

                var signingDateEnd = document.getElementById('signingDateEnd');
                signingDateEnd.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });
                var txtClientName = document.getElementById('txtClientName');
                txtClientName.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });

                var searchClientNumber = document.getElementById('searchClientNumber');
                searchClientNumber.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });

                var txtNumJVPartnersStart = document.getElementById('txtNumJVPartnersStart');
                txtNumJVPartnersStart.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });

                var txtNumJVPartnersEnd = document.getElementById('txtNumJVPartnersEnd');
                txtNumJVPartnersEnd.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });

                var txtJVOwnedByClientStart = document.getElementById('txtJVOwnedByClientStart');
                txtJVOwnedByClientStart.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });

                var txtJVOwnedByClientEnd = document.getElementById('txtJVOwnedByClientEnd');
                txtJVOwnedByClientEnd.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });


                var txtSizeofMinorityStart = document.getElementById('txtSizeofMinorityStart');
                txtSizeofMinorityStart.addEventListener('keypress', function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        document.getElementById('btnSearch').click();
                    }
                });

        });



        $('#createSearchLinkModal').on('hidden.bs.modal', function (event) {
            // Destroy modal
            $(this).removeData('bs.modal');
            $('#modal-container .modal-content').empty();
        });

        $('#dealModal').on('hidden.bs.modal', function (event) {
            // Destroy modal
            $(this).removeData('bs.modal');
            $('#modal-container .modal-content').empty();
        });


        $("#btnCloseLink").click(function () {
            $('#createSearchLinkModal').modal('hide');
        });

        $("#btnXLink").click(function () {
            $('#createSearchLinkModal').modal('hide');
        });
        $("#btnCloseDetailsX").click(function () {
            $('#dealModal').modal('hide');
        });
        $("#btnCloseDetails").click(function () {
            $('#dealModal').modal('hide');
        });
